Author: DACSEE_official
Title: [ANN] DACSEE - Decentralized Alternative Cabs Serving & Empowering Everyone
Body: The DACSEE team is excited to announce that DACSEE token will be listed on QRYPTOS Exchange by QUOINE on July 30, 2018. QUOINE is the first global cryptocurrency firm in the world to be officially licensed by the Japan Financial Services Agency (License 0002).  The DACSEE ICO was set to end on May 31, 2018. We have had tremendous requests from different regions around the world to become a part of the fast growing DACSEE community. To allow more people the opportunity to join our community, we have decided to extend our ICO until July 23, 2018.  DACSEE’s commitment to our early contributors is very important and in this regard our initial listing date target of July remains unchanged. The DACSEE team would like to express our sincere gratitude to all our community members helping us to create a truly decentralized ride sharing platform together.

Body: Thankyou for your interested in DACSEE. Here is a few information regarding DACSEE project. Also, please join our social media to get the mot updated news !   The DACSEE platform ("Decentralized Alternative Cabs Serving & Empowering Everyone") is the world’s first fully decentralized and autonomous social ride-sharing service. DACSEE drivers purchase DACSEE Coin (a cryptocurrency token on the Ethereum blockchain) but may accept fares from passengers with the same token or any other traditional fiat method. When a fare is collected, almost all of it is returned to the platform stakeholders which consists of drivers, passengers and government authorities. This unique design enables DACSEE to expand virally without assistance or control from any corporate entity. The peer-to-peer payment methods and ability for drivers to use the platform to foster their own income-producing Circle of Friends™ of drivers allows DACSEE to spread autonomously into new markets around the world, disrupting the current ride-hailing landscape.

Author: monstrs
Title: [ANN] DACSEE - Decentralized Alternative Cabs Serving & Empowering Everyone
Body: Website | Bounty Campaign | Blog | Facebook | Twitter | YouTube TELEGRAM CHATS:  Dacsee English | Dacsee Japan | Dacsee Indonesia | Dacsee Malayisa | Dacsee Korea     PROBLEM   Modern ride-hailing applications have brought new solutions to the basic human need for travelling, but have also resulted in a market controlled by unsustainable, power-grabbing corporations that disenfranchise the riders and passengers and take an enormous and regularly increasing middlemen  fee from both sides of every transaction.    SOLUTION    The DACSEE platform returns the power and control back to the people and utilises the newest trends  and technology in the decentralisation and cryptocurrency spheres to create a self-regulating and self-expanding ridesharing network that requires no central authority and therefore no middlemen fees. This peer-topeer system brings the sharing economy back into the ride-hailing economy and empowers the individuals to create their own incomes unencumbered, in a multitude of ways, while expanding naturally and virally into markets that have thus far been inaccessible to centrally-run ride-hailing services.   Help us to promote this awesome idea and earn up to 55 stakes a weak by joining our Bounty Campaign!  Join our social media channels and together we’ll create  the Ultimate Ride-sharing Platform built by community for the community!
